.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-MEMPOOL-FEES" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-mempool-fees \- show current fee rates from the node
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-mempool-fees
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the current fee rates (perkw) as seen by the CLN node: urgent, normal, slow, min_acceptable, max_acceptable.
.PP
Output: JSON object with fee rate fields in sat/kw.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-check-config (1)
